CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper November 6, 1954, pg. 16, reads: "Leaders at Hill Polls - In the left photo, Mrs. Mary Ellen Pennywell, Edward Robinson and David Thompkins, Fifth Ward Republican chairman are shown near one of the polls last Tuesday morning... Harris Photos."
TitMainTitle: Mary Ellen Pennywell, Edward Robinson, and Fifth Ward Republican chairman David Thompkins standing on sidewalk in front of parked Chevrolet car, near polling place, Hill District
